Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-------------------------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.01,0:00:10.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,双向通信系统 在预定地点全部布设完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.21,0:00:12.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,EURO-2来电
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.21,0:00:16.89,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,EURO-AEU代号 UNIORN-国联代号 HUMAN-人革联代号
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.64,0:00:16.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在开始布设浮游型双向通信系统
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.72,0:00:23.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,UNION-3起的通信网络 接收状况一切正常
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.58,0:00:28.35,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,{\fs20\an2}人革联 塔克拉玛干沙漠驻屯基地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.33,0:00:25.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,测试项目全部通过
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.88,0:00:32.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,参加演习的全体部队 确认通信网络完成连接
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.63,0:00:37.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有MS的通信情况良好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.96,0:00:46.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没想到啊 竟然会有和UNION以及AEU联手的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.64,0:00:51.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得意忘形
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.77,0:00:56.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少尉 机体的防尘状况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.48,0:00:58.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好到不能再好 上校
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.58,0:01:02.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着吧 用这架机体一定能把Gundam…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.20,0:01:02.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.07,0:01:03.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.10,0:01:06.48,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,{\fs20\an2}UNION军 冲绳近海
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.60,0:01:09.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Over Flags队待命
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.68,0:01:10.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.20,0:01:16.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部队总数52支  参战MS 832架
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.94,0:01:22.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别怪我们卑鄙 服从命令是军人的天职
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.17,0:01:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.74,0:01:41.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易丝 你打算站到什么时候呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.85,0:01:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈回去了 人家很消沉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.05,0:01:45.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个我能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.11,0:01:48.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请给我打气
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.35,0:01:49.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打起精神来哦 路易丝…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.47,0:01:52.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请从物质方面 拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.24,0:02:04.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的 路易丝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.71,0:02:07.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种奢侈品 怎么可能买得起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.35,0:02:10.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了我买下来嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.51,0:02:11.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可以
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.34,0:02:13.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,买嘛 买嘛 为了我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.40,0:02:15.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,买给我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.50,0:02:14.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们在闹什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.94,0:02:16.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真悠闲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.87,0:02:21.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在有近千台MS正在进行大规模军事演习呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.23,0:02:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那才是异常的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.28,0:02:32.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次大规模军事演习 也在你的计划之中吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.84,0:02:35.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊奥利亚·舒恩伯格
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.80,0:02:38.68,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,{\fs20\an2}人革联 国家主席官邸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.21,0:02:42.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那件事怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.48,0:02:44.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情报部 报告如下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.56,0:02:52.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如我们所料 有3台MS和运输车辆 正在前往浓缩铀的埋设地区
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.54,0:02:55.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来只需等他们上钩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.81,0:03:00.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.42,0:03:03.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布设在演习地域里的双向通信系统
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.62,0:03:05.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发出了故障反应
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.63,0:03:08.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照计划
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.86,0:03:12.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向司令官传达作战变更命令
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.67,0:03:18.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可是背负着舆论压力提供了演习场所
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.13,0:03:22.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少也得弄到两台
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.38,0:03:27.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿勒路亚 维持速度和高度
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.78,0:03:32.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别让机体晃动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.90,0:03:34.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别要求太高
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.48,0:03:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,观测班 Gundam的目标是哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.70,0:03:44.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在通信故障的方向上 没有驻屯部队
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.81,0:03:47.29,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AEU塔克拉玛干沙漠前线基地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.37,0:03:52.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 Gundam正在接近浓缩铀的埋设地域？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.08,0:03:56.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事 为什么没有注意到恐怖分子接近设施
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.15,0:03:57.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么没有发现
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.66,0:04:01.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中校 司令部发来命令俘获Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.31,0:04:02.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.54,0:04:05.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.05,0:04:08.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一切全是事先设计好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.98,0:04:23.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说为诱出Gundam 政府明知恐怖分子的行动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.05,0:04:26.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故意放弃设施
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.17,0:04:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dynames 狙击目标
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.91,0:04:50.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全弹命中 全弹命中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.14,0:04:51.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要撤离了 阿勒路亚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.75,0:04:52.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.12,0:04:57.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌袭！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.76,0:05:04.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌机接近 敌机接近
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.80,0:05:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.45,0:05:10.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.26,0:05:11.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.88,0:05:31.77,Second,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌机接近 敌机接近
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.10,0:05:30.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿勒路亚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.03,0:05:37.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.85,0:05:41.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.61,0:05:57.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.33,0:05:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.70,0:06:00.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.31,0:06:13.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炮击一刻都不能松懈 牵制住Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.74,0:06:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一阶段的预定结束时间过了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.54,0:06:50.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望他们已经安全撤离了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.94,0:06:53.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇小姐的预测呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.34,0:06:58.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕事态正向B2计划转移
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.76,0:07:03.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exia和Virtur的投入
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.97,0:07:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,UNION-3 第一波攻击成功
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.40,0:07:09.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两台Gundam位于TF4122区域
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.24,0:07:10.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续远程炮击
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.03,0:07:13.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白 继续远程炮击
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.16,0:07:15.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HUMAN-1传来可视暗号
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.05,0:07:18.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要求派部队前往TF2123地区
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.04,0:07:21.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然选择了薄弱的地点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.24,0:07:25.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出动第二十三MS部队
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.71,0:07:28.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二十三MS部队 出击
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.91,0:07:31.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二十三MS部队 出击
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.13,0:07:36.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大校 为什么不命令我出击
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.97,0:07:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去抓Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.35,0:07:39.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你暂时待机
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.54,0:07:40.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.51,0:07:41.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.96,0:07:44.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会让你成为一个男人的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.63,0:07:52.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任务计划变更为B2
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.85,0:07:54.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.15,0:07:57.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exia 外壁迷彩膜解冻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.36,0:07:59.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任务开始
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.37,0:08:07.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现两台Gundam 快联络总部
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.20,0:08:29.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Virtur 确保撤退路线
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.12,0:08:33.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN火箭炮 轰炸模式
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.11,0:08:42.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粒子压缩率 97%
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.67,0:08:45.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN粒子 释放
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.97,0:09:02.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提耶利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.42,0:09:04.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,计划转移为B2了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.52,0:09:05.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤离 阿勒路亚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.90,0:09:07.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.41,0:09:11.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首弹发射完成
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.13,0:09:14.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN粒子开始充填
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.22,0:09:22.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这数量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.51,0:09:24.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应对真快
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.95,0:09:36.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作战开始后已经过去两个小时了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.43,0:09:42.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按B2计划的话 Dynames和Kyrios应该即将到达汇合地点了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.59,0:09:47.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能使用GN ARMS也好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.41,0:09:51.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从时间上判断 应该是从B2转移到E5了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.56,0:09:57.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是这样的话 那架机体应该来了 阿勒路亚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.54,0:10:05.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 阿勒路亚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.94,0:10:07.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脑袋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.47,0:10:12.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了 超兵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.02,0:10:13.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说超兵？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.41,0:10:16.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报告里提到的人革联专用机吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.87,0:10:17.81,Second,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌机接近 敌机接近
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.82,0:10:41.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.05,0:10:55.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿勒路亚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.06,0:10:58.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正中下怀吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.77,0:11:14.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提耶利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.21,0:11:16.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,充填还要多久
