Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.95,0:12:08.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 真无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.50,0:12:11.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面就交给你了 阿勒路亚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.35,0:12:13.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈雷路亚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.59,0:12:24.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗开始后已经过了5个小时了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.70,0:12:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去哪里
