Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.82,0:14:21.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别被敌人的光束击中啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.05,0:14:32.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 战斗开始后已经15个小时了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.42,0:14:47.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.29,0:14:49.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炮击停了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.91,0:14:51.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤离
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.23,0:14:51.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.42,0:15:04.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到你了 Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.79,0:15:16.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦 你的动作很迟钝嘛 Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.53,0:15:17.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.30,0:15:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam到手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.73,0:15:33.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.10,0:15:36.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这都多亏了本大爷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.60,0:15:41.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中校 已俘获带翼机
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.39,0:15:42.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意点 少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.75,0:15:45.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定还会像以前那样突然启动
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.02,0:15:47.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.02,0:15:58.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指挥官 已视线确认目标
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.06,0:16:00.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进入作战行动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.21,0:16:02.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Over Flags
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.31,0:16:04.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,E阵形开始任务
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.64,0:16:06.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长 约书亚他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.38,0:16:09.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约书亚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.11,0:16:10.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别打乱阵形
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.27,0:16:13.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真当你是队长了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.73,0:16:18.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空中变形?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.38,0:16:22.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别以为你又能独占
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.85,0:16:25.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…啊 …什么?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.60,0:16:30.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约书亚他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.23,0:16:33.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阵形变更为C
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.49,0:16:41.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指尖的感觉已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.82,0:16:46.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想抱紧你啊 Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.32,0:16:57.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直就是 睡美人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.64,0:16:59.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲尔德
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.98,0:17:01.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Meister他们有联系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.92,0:17:03.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.84,0:17:05.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.15,0:17:11.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在消失
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.57,0:17:15.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam Meister的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.10,0:17:21.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他的Meister们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.77,0:17:27.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三点钟方向 出现敌影
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.35,0:17:33.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mobile Armor
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.05,0:17:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那台Enact是…!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.85,0:17:39.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来清算上次那笔债了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.49,0:17:41.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样啊Gundam老兄
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.64,0:18:06.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.88,0:18:18.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,味道如何啊 Agristor的等离子护罩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.81,0:18:21.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机体留下 你去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.42,0:18:23.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,库尔吉斯的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.99,0:18:33.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外交部的非正式情报称
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.76,0:18:37.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚欧大陆上进行的联合演习中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.56,0:18:40.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「天人」组织出现了
