Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.51,0:18:48.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 只用四台Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.02,0:18:51.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就来挑战近千台MS部队什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.70,0:18:53.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太胡来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.16,0:18:57.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.65,0:19:00.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.94,0:19:06.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何 这个世界如此扭曲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.55,0:19:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是神真主的错吗 还是人的错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.26,0:19:13.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道当时…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.97,0:19:15.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.58,0:19:26.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.63,0:19:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会死吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.77,0:19:32.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这个扭曲的世界之中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.67,0:19:36.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一无所成
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.53,0:19:39.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去一切
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.56,0:19:43.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,默默无闻地死去
