Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.62,0:19:57.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GUN…DAM
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.97,0:20:04.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.09,0:20:15.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.67,0:20:23.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么!?
