Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.24,0:21:23.51,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}即使告诉我你的勇气　即使逞强
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.60,0:21:28.31,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}一个人便无法生存下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.89,0:21:32.66,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}那一日的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.87,0:21:37.78,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}于我心深处　只步未移
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.95,0:21:42.69,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}As life goes on...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.20,0:21:48.48,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}因为不能忘记 Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.61,0:21:53.29,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Don't let it go...
